      "l1": " was paid, the whole order seemed to vanish from his memory. Her name was Bluma Zeigarnik, and she turned this small observation into a famous idea. Our "
    },
    {
      "t": "weave",
      "l1": "brain",
      "l2": "Gehirn",
      "lemma": "Gehirn",
      "pos": "noun",
      "gender": "n",
